\begin_inset Formula $\left|\left\langle a_{1}(b_{1}+b_{2})+a_{2}(b_{1}-b_{2})\right\rangle \right|\equiv\left|\left\langle C(a_{i},b_{i})\right\rangle \right|\le2$
